data.description: Welcome home to Ocean Springs, named the nation's ''best coastal small town'' and listed in Southern Living as one of the ''best places to retire in the south'' This tri-level house is within the downtown Ocean Springs golf cart district and is just blocks away from Gulf Islands National Seashore.  Also, it is a 5 minute walk to Pecan Park Elementary, located in the sought after ''A Rated'' Ocean Springs school district in the state.  Inside, you'll absolutely love the open concept kitchen with an abundance of beautiful cabinetry and lighting. The French doors open up to the large deck that is perfect for relaxing or game day cookouts.  On the upper level you'll find a primary bedroom, two secondary bedrooms and two full baths. The lower level is used as a den and playroom but has endless possibilities for use with its spacious layout and half bath.  The roof was replaced in 2022, new windows installed in 2023, and the crawl space was encapsulated in 2020.  The opportunity to own your home in this beautiful coastal town with picturesque sunsets, white sandy beaches, culturally rich history, and southern hospitality will not last long! Call your Realtor today for your private tour!
